title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-24-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-24-2013 TUES




The Glenn Beck Program



          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/24/13Tuesday, December 24, 2013 10:44 AM




Buck is back filling in for Glenn on this Christmas Eve show
    and he's got a Christmas story you don't want to miss,
      that involves one of our greatest founding fathers.

         Also, a Buck brief about the current situation in the Middle East
            and the dangerous the global community is facing from the events
               occurring in this historically volatile part of the world,


  Plus, a history lesson on Christmas, 
       why we celebrate the way we do and where these traditions originated.
